            "text": "{\"activities\": [{\"id\":17716528600244,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82207208810},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:40Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_counter_group_transfer\":\"5\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528589460,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82007884864},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_reassigned_time\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528587050,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000717524,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Group reassignment is >3 | Council SLA changes | ACE TS\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":11,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"group_name\":\"TS_ACE Payments\",\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_breach_category\":\"Multi-transfer\",\"cf_parents_group\":\"Ace groups\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528586990,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000711382,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Council - Child ticket reopened| reassignment status change[Tech support]\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":6,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"status\":2,\"status_label\":\"Open\",\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_end_state_action\":null}}}]},{\"id\":17716528586975,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000695374,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Reassigned from update - CS tickets\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_reassigned_from\":\"CS\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528586688,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000711354,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Reassigned to Tech Support | Open status\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":6,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"status\":2,\"status_label\":\"Open\"}}]},{\"id\":17716528586671,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000712333,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Reassignment BSO to Tech\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_reassigned_ticket\":\"BSO to Tech\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528586403,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":0,\"type\":\"round_robin\",\"name\":\"\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":37,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"round_robin\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":82208991420}}]},{\"id\":17716528586120,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000712360,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Reassigned to different groups| Restriction of valid reassignment fields\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_reassigned_ticket\":null}}}]},{\"id\":17716528586107,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000695321,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Function update - Best tickets\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:38Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_function\":\"BEST\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528549510,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82007884864},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:34Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_recent_agent_response_time\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528545111,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000695321,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Function update - Best tickets\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:34Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_function\":\"BEST\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528510000,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82218776560},\"highlight\":36,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:31Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"note\",\"content\":{\"body\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px\\\">\\n<div>Dear Vann,</div>\\n<div> </div>\\n<div>Thank you for reaching out regarding your request to increase transaction limits to 10 lakhs for both national and international transactions. We’ve also taken note of the error you faced while attempting to update these limits on the dashboard.</div>\\n<div> </div>\\n<div>Your ticket (ID: #18125250) has been escalated to our technical team for a thorough review. You’ll receive an update and a resolution within 24 hours.</div>\\n<div> </div>\\n<div>Meanwhile, if you require any additional help, you can access our support resources at <a href=\\\"https://razorpay.com/support/\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer\\\">Razorpay Support</a>.</div>\\n<div> </div>\\n<div>Regards,</div>\\n<div>Rishika Biswakarma</div>\\n<div>Team Razorpay</div>\\n</div>\",\"body_text\":\"Dear Vann,     Thank you for reaching out regarding your request to increase transaction limits to 10 lakhs for both national and international transactions. We’ve also taken note of the error you faced while attempting to update these limits on the dashboard.     Your ticket (ID: #18125250) has been escalated to our technical team for a thorough review. You’ll receive an update and a resolution within 24 hours.     Meanwhile, if you require any additional help, you can access our support resources at Razorpay Support.     Regards,  Rishika Biswakarma  Team Razorpay\",\"structured_body\":null,\"id\":83226935646,\"incoming\":false,\"private\":false,\"user_id\":82218776560,\"support_email\":\"rzr06py08emsp@razorpay.com\",\"source\":0,\"category\":3,\"to_emails\":[\"van@arlox.io\"],\"from_email\":\"\\\"Razorpay support\\\" <rzr06py08emsp@razorpay.com>\",\"cc_emails\":[],\"bcc_emails\":[],\"email_failure_count\":0,\"outgoing_failures\":null,\"thread_id\":null,\"thread_message_id\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:31Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:31Z\",\"last_edited_at\":null,\"last_edited_user_id\":0,\"attachments\":[],\"automation_id\":null,\"automation_type_id\":null,\"automation_channel_type\":null,\"auto_response\":false,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"threading_type\":null,\"delivery_details\":{\"failed_emails\":[],\"pending_emails\":[]},\"deleted\":false,\"cloud_files\":[],\"has_quoted_text\":true}}]},{\"id\":17716528505769,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82207208810},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:30Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_counter_group_transfer\":\"4\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716528490879,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82218776560},\"highlight\":9,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:29Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":null,\"group_name\":\"TS_Payments\"}}]},{\"id\":17716528339866,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82007884864},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:47:13Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_canned_response_id\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716526989732,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82007884864},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:44:58Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_canned_response_id\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716526713402,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82218776560},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:44:31Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_created_by\":\"merchant\",\"cf_contact_number\":\"*\",\"cf_end_state_action\":\"Transfer To A Different Group\",\"cf_valid_reassignment\":\"No\"}}}]},{\"id\":17716526560000,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82218776560},\"highlight\":36,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:44:16Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"note\",\"content\":{\"body\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px\\\">\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Please read the below mentioned note of mx as they are facing error while submitting request so take this forward from your end.</div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><br></div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><br></div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><br></div>\\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; padding: 12px 16px 16px; min-height: 65px; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", Roboto, Arial, \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial'><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; width: 1181px\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 16px; width: 1181px\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: flex; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; flex-wrap: wrap\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block; padding-right: 3px\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; display: inline-block\\\"><a href=\\\"https://razorpay-ind.freshdesk.com/a/contacts/82072804228\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(44, 92, 197); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer\\\">Laniakea Enterprises LLP</a></div></div></div>\\n<span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding-left: 3px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(24, 50, 71)\\\">replied</span>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 5px; align-items: center\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left; font-size: 12px; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(71, 88, 103)\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block\\\">2 days ago <span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; display: inline-block\\\">(Thu, 19 Feb 2026 at 5:53 PM)</span></span></span></div></div>\\n</div>\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; float: right; padding: 0px; margin: 0px\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px 0px; color: rgb(187, 220, 254); opacity: 1; right: 16px; line-height: 0; font-size: 0px; top: 16px\\\"> </div></div>\\n</div></div>\\n<div style='box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 16px 16px 48px; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", Roboto, Arial, \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial'><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 15px; margin-bottom: 14px\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; float: left !important; margin-right: 12px\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); width: 305.406px; display: inline-block\\\">\\n<span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 500; float: left\\\">To:</span><span style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-left: 4px\\\">\\\"Razorpay support\\\" &lt;rzr06py08emsp@razorpay.com&gt;</span>\\n</div></div></div>\\n<div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; cursor: auto; color: rgb(24, 50, 71); margin: 0px; padding: 0px\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px 16px; overflow: auto hidden\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word\\\"><div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word\\\">Dear Team Razorpay,<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">I am writing to follow up on my previous request regarding the transaction limit increase for my account (Ticket ID: #18045214).<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">We have partnered with Razorpay for the last five years without issue, and I have always valued the professional and proactive support your team provided. However, my recent experience has been disappointing. Receiving automated replies and generic directives to read the website—rather than addressing the technical errors I have reported—is hindering our operations.<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">Please be advised that if the limit for both national and international transactions is not increased to 10 lakhs immediately, we will be forced to explore alternative payment providers. Given our transaction volume, this would result in a loss of over ₹30,000 in fees per transaction for your platform.<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">I urge you to resolve the technical issues I am facing on the dashboard and proceed with the requested limit increase.<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">Regards,<br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\"><br style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box\\\">Vann Laniakea</div></div></div></div></div>\\n</div></div>\\n</div>\",\"body_text\":\"Please read the below mentioned note of mx as they are facing error while submitting request so take this forward from your end.                 Laniakea Enterprises LLP   replied   2 days ago (Thu, 19 Feb 2026 at 5:53 PM)               To:\\\"Razorpay support\\\" <rzr06py08emsp@razorpay.com>        Dear Team Razorpay,  I am writing to follow up on my previous request regarding the transaction limit increase for my account (Ticket ID: #18045214).  We have partnered with Razorpay for the last five years without issue, and I have always valued the professional and proactive support your team provided. However, my recent experience has been disappointing. Receiving automated replies and generic directives to read the website—rather than addressing the technical errors I have reported—is hindering our operations.  Please be advised that if the limit for both national and international transactions is not increased to 10 lakhs immediately, we will be forced to explore alternative payment providers. Given our transaction volume, this would result in a loss of over ₹30,000 in fees per transaction for your platform.  I urge you to resolve the technical issues I am facing on the dashboard and proceed with the requested limit increase.  Regards,  Vann Laniakea\",\"structured_body\":null,\"id\":83226933606,\"incoming\":false,\"private\":true,\"user_id\":82218776560,\"support_email\":null,\"source\":2,\"category\":2,\"to_emails\":[],\"from_email\":null,\"cc_emails\":[],\"bcc_emails\":null,\"email_failure_count\":null,\"outgoing_failures\":null,\"thread_id\":null,\"thread_message_id\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:44:16Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-21T05:44:16Z\",\"last_edited_at\":null,\"last_edited_user_id\":null,\"attachments\":[],\"automation_id\":null,\"automation_type_id\":null,\"automation_channel_type\":null,\"auto_response\":false,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"threading_type\":null,\"delivery_details\":{\"failed_emails\":[],\"pending_emails\":[]},\"deleted\":false,\"cloud_files\":[],\"has_quoted_text\":false}}]}],\"meta\": {\"count\":73}}"
