            "text": "{\"activities\": [{\"id\":17715679937248,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82207208810},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:13:13Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_counter_group_transfer\":\"2\"}}}]},{\"id\":17715679924433,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82212257718},\"highlight\":9,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:13:12Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":null,\"group_name\":\"TS_Payments\",\"due_by\":\"2026-02-23T08:17:12Z\"}}]},{\"id\":17715679170000,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82212257718},\"highlight\":36,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:11:57Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"note\",\"content\":{\"body\":\"<div style=\\\"font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:14px\\\">\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\">HI team,</div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><br></div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\">Merchant trying to submit a request from the dashboard to raise the transaction limit but encountering a technical issue while submitting. A screenshot has been provided by MX for  review. Please check this further.</div>\\n</div>\",\"body_text\":\"HI team,     Merchant trying to submit a request from the dashboard to raise the transaction limit but encountering a technical issue while submitting. A screenshot has been provided by MX for  review. Please check this further.\",\"structured_body\":null,\"id\":83226469608,\"incoming\":false,\"private\":true,\"user_id\":82212257718,\"support_email\":null,\"source\":2,\"category\":2,\"to_emails\":[],\"from_email\":null,\"cc_emails\":[],\"bcc_emails\":null,\"email_failure_count\":null,\"outgoing_failures\":null,\"thread_id\":null,\"thread_message_id\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:11:57Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:11:57Z\",\"last_edited_at\":null,\"last_edited_user_id\":null,\"attachments\":[{\"id\":82200833546,\"name\":\"Screenshot 2026-02-12 at 3.04.55 PM.png\",\"content_type\":\"image/png\",\"size\":55167,\"created_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:11:43Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:11:57Z\",\"attachment_url\":\"https://razorpay-ind.attachments-ind2.freshdesk.com/data/helpdesk/attachments/production/82200833546/original/Screenshot%202026-02-12%20at%203.04.55%E2%80%AFPM.png?Expires=1771781111&Signature=XpAYgx1~5YI4HubIBC72VvSwGDBhoUB5TDyDrPzDpAHiYqJ85AiqhKOcsehip0Q2gzPSYtFDZFmYVzfLlJeS1H3~svcOqdLdAPO~F2kONvprXYDRj21me7kzx54svBVNkVyMtCTJM9DW~dYuZ2Fe2LWRqn0femfnf7982DbwqSvB12EaGmIUdewiG2TWIPWHNcHHFdX0I~Yw8pApJ1fQsGN-R-h23xUJ8pmml00fv5qVbcIiaYATvEFmzjB0AZzof1zMvv5DKORltHQfxP4lsZFa0Ih~iT2WzWXJ7sMFM8uKIzoZOJQkbbFRi5YOLNBSgi1JPd0lhPcvQntTLGDasA__&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJ7JARUX3F6RQIXLA\",\"thumb_url\":\"https://razorpay-ind.attachments-ind2.freshdesk.com/data/helpdesk/attachments/production/82200833546/thumb/Screenshot%202026-02-12%20at%203.04.55%E2%80%AFPM.png?Expires=1771781111&Signature=MvKTPSCk8y0lpw80wR9QnaQ8ANMKAGU2wJQSX6s2QD90KjQ2Zv5i1~lMaCBSmYehJQO1PjjmCey3u2H26X~ZOK4X-2qMRo3hbjiZZMi2NanrmRuh9gl-n8fZ3Jtkl8ZCZkw4JNb5dZ-FQJHbGA7lz2eNE5smRaZ48v74Lc0zx52sYjaRJVsKEKqM7Pwevnu7t2xAyrQwZvXS08RYPh-rLQxFN48t4jA1QUtCl4oGd6YnGYGodCQZvYNzkV5wcr0aaxc7wRXaS6h88BGEAVIPzwzgsO1DajcASRIoWyQKzWjmT9byP3YvQIGGxdHTL8wc1SN9q0yABZKJfqJ4lX9wOw__&Key-Pair-Id=APKAJ7JARUX3F6RQIXLA\"}],\"automation_id\":null,\"automation_type_id\":null,\"automation_channel_type\":null,\"auto_response\":false,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"threading_type\":null,\"delivery_details\":{\"failed_emails\":[],\"pending_emails\":[]},\"deleted\":false,\"cloud_files\":[],\"has_quoted_text\":false}}]},{\"id\":17715672495495,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82173666232},\"highlight\":8,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-20T06:00:49Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":82212257718}}]},{\"id\":17715549256752,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":0,\"type\":\"round_robin\",\"name\":\"\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":37,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-20T02:35:25Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"round_robin\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":82173666232}}]},{\"id\":17715143434645,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000694427,\"type\":\"supervisor\",\"name\":\"First Response Due\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":18,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T15:19:03Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"add_tag\",\"content\":[\"First Response SLA\"]},{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_sla_breach\":\"First Response SLA\"}}}]},{\"id\":17715126671710,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82156007164},\"highlight\":9,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T14:51:07Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":null}}]},{\"id\":17715072962366,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82220578819},\"highlight\":8,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T13:21:36Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"responder_id\":82232781986}}]},{\"id\":17715037933962,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82007884864},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T12:23:13Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_recent_customer_response_time\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17715037930015,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"system\",\"system\":{\"id\":82000691783,\"type\":\"observer\",\"name\":\"Social Media - >1 Iteration\",\"exists\":true}},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T12:23:13Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_predictive_escalation\":\"Yes\"}}}]},{\"id\":17715037926979,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82207208810},\"highlight\":40,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T12:23:12Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"property_update\",\"content\":{\"custom_fields\":{\"cf_merchant_interaction\":\"*\"}}}]},{\"id\":17715037900000,\"performer\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"user_id\":82072804228},\"highlight\":36,\"ticket_id\":18125250,\"performed_at\":\"2026-02-19T12:23:10Z\",\"actions\":[{\"type\":\"note\",\"content\":{\"body\":\"<div dir=\\\"auto\\\">Dear Team Razorpay,<br><br>I am writing to follow up on my previous request regarding the transaction limit increase for my account (Ticket ID: #18045214).<br><br>We have partnered with Razorpay for the last five years without issue, and I have always valued the professional and proactive support your team provided. However, my recent experience has been disappointing. Receiving automated replies and generic directives to read the website—rather than addressing the technical errors I have reported—is hindering our operations.<br><br>Please be advised that if the limit for both national and international transactions is not increased to 10 lakhs immediately, we will be forced to explore alternative payment providers. Given our transaction volume, this would result in a loss of over ₹30,000 in fees per transaction for your platform.<br><br>I urge you to resolve the technical issues I am facing on the dashboard and proceed with the requested limit increase.<br><br>Regards,<br><br>Vann Laniakea<div><br></div>\\n<div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" class=\\\"gmail_signature\\\"><div dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\n<div style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><font style=\\\"font-family:verdana,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)\\\"><br></font></div>\\n<table cellpadding=\\\"0\\\" cellspacing=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"border-spacing:0px;border-collapse:collapse;width:480px;font-size:9pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:14px;color:rgb(68,68,68)\\\"><tbody style=\\\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\\\">\\n<tr style=\\\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif\\\"><td colspan=\\\"2\\\" style=\\\"padding:0px 0px 5px;width:480px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(60,60,59)\\\"><sp