,Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote class=\\\"gmail_quote\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>     <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'></div> </div></blockquote></blockquote></div></blockquote></div></div></div> <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><blockquote class=\\\"gmail_quote\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Dear Partner,</div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box\\\"></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Greetings for the day!</div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>As we talked about during the call concerning the limit increase, please follow these steps below.</div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>1. Navigate to the Account and Settings section on your dashboard.<br>2. Go to Payments and refunds.<br>3. Select Transaction limits.<br>4. Click on the pencil option on the right corner of the option Limit per domestic transaction.<br>5. Update the relevant fields and submit the request for verification.</div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>After the request has been submitted, our team will provide you with an update within 24 to 48 hours.</div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Note: Only the owner and the administrator are allowed to submit the request from the dashboard.</div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>I am forwarding your additional concern regarding the partnership program to the relevant team, and they will provide you with an update within 24 to 48 hours.</div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><span rel=\\\"tempredactor\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>The ticket reference for your request is #18045214.</span></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></div>    </div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div dir=\\\"ltr\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><span style='box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-word;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><span style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Visit our help page : </span><a href=\\\"https://razorpay.com/support/\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer\\\" title=\\\"https://razorpay.com/support/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><u style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>https://razorpay.com/support/</u></a></span></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><span style='box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-word;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br></span></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><span style='box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-word;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Regards,</span></div>    <table style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><tbody style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><tr style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <td style='box-sizing:border-box;padding:5pt;min-width:5px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><div style='box-sizing:border-box;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <span style='box-sizing:border-box;word-break:normal;font-size:9pt;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><img src=\\\"https://indattachment.freshdesk.com/inline/attachment?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpZCI6ODIxODg0NTA0NDYsImRvbWFpbiI6InJhem9ycGF5LWluZC5mcmVzaGRlc2suY29tIiwiYWNjb3VudF9pZCI6MTcyMjEwNn0.B_I7wb4KjQaCuuNiyDF3UZp0Hrlfox--IjHlz-9jTlc\\\" width=\\\"135\\\" height=\\\"30\\\" alt=\\\"rzp-logo-positive-for-email-signature@2x.png\\\" style='box-sizing: border-box; border-width: initial; border-style: none; padding-right: 1px; padding-left: 1px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\\"Segoe UI\\\", Roboto, \\\"Helvetica Neue\\\", Arial, sans-serif'></span><span style='box-sizing:border-box;word-break:normal;font-size:9pt;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><br style=\\\"box-sizing:border-box\\\"></span><span style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>The Future of Payments is Here</span>    </div></td>    <td style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'><font style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(0,0,0)'><strong style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,\\\"Helvetica Neue\\\",Arial,sans-serif'>Pratham Varshney</strong></font></div>    <div style='font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,